parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft position sensor can cause the engine to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. It can also cause the check engine light to come on, which can lead to further engine damage if not addressed.
symptoms: The engine stalls
the check engine light comes on
the vehicle runs hot
the horn stays on and won't go off
the vehicle idles high and then goes back down
there is a burning smell coming from under the hood
and smoke can be seen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to obtain recall repairs can lead to continued engine problems, stalling, and potential accidents.
symptoms: Difficulty finding an authorized dealer to perform the recall
dealers refusing to honor the recall
no parts available
dealerships out of business
and phone numbers provided in the recall letter being out of service.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine problems can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine blows up
the timing belt breaks
the seat belts do not work properly
and the engine sounds like a diesel engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hose can cause a loss of brake pressure, leading to a loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries.
symptoms: Squealing noise when applying the brakes
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal loses pressure
brakes lock up
tires spin out of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake rotors can cause a loss of braking performance, leading to accidents and potential injuries.
symptoms: Loud noise when applying the brakes
rotors are soft and cannot be turned
brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause a loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries.
symptoms: Loss of brake pressure
brakes lock up
tires spin out of control
vehicle spins out of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various accessories to malfunction, including the cruise control, air conditioning, dashboard lights, and headlights, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: Cruise control doesn't work
air conditioning works intermittently
dashboard lights and clock don't function
key cannot be removed from ignition
shift lock stays engaged
headlights go out intermittently
power accessories and horn are inoperative.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the key to become extremely hot, which can lead to burns or fires.
symptoms: Key is burning hot when removed from ignition.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the spark plug wire housing can cause a fire, which can lead to serious safety risks.
symptoms: Screws that hold the plastic housing over the spark plug wires fall off
plastic falls on the engine and catches on fire.
